commit.message:
Append to config if it doesn't already have `contents` (#21)

* Append to config if it doesn't already have `contents`

* Add a test for prepending the same location twice

MANIFEST.in: Add tests to sdist (#13)

Fixes https://github.com/ofek/userpath/issues/11

HISTORY.rst: Include history of adduserpath (#14)

Package adduserpath is part of the history, distributed
via PyPI and packaged and distributed by Fedora.

Closes https://github.com/ofek/userpath/issues/12

Make distro dependency optional (#16)

The distro package only supports Linux, and it is only used
here to detect Ubuntu.  Make it an optional dependency in the
code, so that packagers can exclude it when it isnt needed.

Closes https://github.com/ofek/userpath/issues/15
